<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>

<head>
	<%- include('./template/head')%>
</head>

<body>
	<%- include('./template/navbar')%>
	<section class='section__lottery'>
		<div class='lottery__bg'>
			<div class='lottery__body'>
				<h2 class='lottery__title'>2020 夏日輕盈特賞！ 抽獎活動辦法</h2>
				<div class='lottery__info'>
					<div class='lottery__row'>
						<div class='lottery__header'>活動期間：</div>
						<div class='lottery__text'>2020/06/01~2020/07/01</div>
					</div> <!-- end .lottery__row -->
					<div class='lottery__row'>
						<div class='lottery__header'>活動說明：</div>
						<div class='lottery__text'>今天老闆佛心來著決定給大家發獎勵，有看有機會，沒看只能幫QQ！只要在店內消費滿1000000元即有機會獲得 - 頭獎日本東京來回雙人遊！</div>
					</div>
					<div class='lottery__row'>
						<div class='lottery__header'>獎  品：</div>
						<div class='lottery__text'>
							<% for (let i=1; i < prize.length ; i++) { %>
							❤ <%= prize[i].prizeName%> <%= prize[i].prizeAmount%> 名：<%= prize[i].prizeItem%>（<%= prize[i].prizeDesc%>）<br>
							<% } %>
					</div>
				</div>
				<a href='./draw-lottery'><input type='button' class='lottery__btn lottery__btn-drawing' value='我要抽獎'></input></a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
	<%- include('./template/footer')%>
</body>

</html>